body: What do you mean? The latest version won't work?
Also can I have a sample of the said output?

Last version of waifu2x-ncnn-vulkan does not work with thoose GPU. Video2x runs to the end of the program but the output video is not the result wanted.
You need to use 20200223 version of waifu2x-ncnn-vulkan (the link) to temporary solve the issue.
I copied this version on the folder video2x-4.0.0_beta4-win32-full\dependencies and i cliced on "replace same named files" during the copying.

It's a waifu2x-ncnn-vulkan bug, not video2x.

https://github.com/nihui/waifu2x-ncnn-vulkan/issues/59
I see. You can fix that temporarily by downloading w2x manually and replace the folder in dependencies. I'll change the file in the release as well. Thanks for letting me know.

I have a GTX 1060 6G, and the latest release seems fine with me.
